@startuml
!option handwritten true
actor "管理员" as Admin
participant "管理平台" as Platform
participant "线程池" as ThreadPool
participant "阻塞队列" as Queue
actor "客户端" as Client

== 固定容量场景（容量=1000） ==
Client -> ThreadPool: 提交任务 (流量激增)
ThreadPool -> Queue: 放入任务
Queue -> ThreadPool: 队列已满 (容量=1000)
ThreadPool -> Client: 拒绝任务
note right: 固定容量可能引发系统雪崩

== 动态扩容场景 ==
Admin -> Platform: 请求调整队列容量
Platform -> Queue: setCapacity(10000)
Queue -> Queue: 更新容量为 10000
Queue -> Platform: 容量调整成功
Platform -> Admin: 确认容量变更
note right: 管理平台触发动态扩容

Client -> ThreadPool: 提交任务 (流量激增)
ThreadPool -> Queue: 放入任务
Queue -> ThreadPool: 任务成功排队
note right: 扩容后缓冲流量高峰，避免任务拒绝

@enduml